Installation
=================
Install JDK and JRE
Install Maven
Setup Variables for both Java and Maven
Install Jenkins.msi file > Enjoy


Links
=================
GIT download
https://git-scm.com/downloads
JDK download
https://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/jdk8-downloads-2133151.html
War file download
https://jenkins.io/download/
MVN Download
https://maven.apache.org/download.cgi


Changing Jenkin Ports
=================
Go to the directory where you installed Jenkins (C:\Program Files\Jenkins)
Open Jenkins.xml
Search --httpPort=8080 and replace the 8080 with the new port number that you wish (i.e. 8099)
Then, restart Jenkins for changes to take effect using below method

Restart Jenkins
=================
Press Win + R
Type "services.msc"
Right click on the "Jenkins" line > Restart
